node.text:
Big shout out to all of YOU….the music lovers, the fans, for the many years of support that you not only have shown to me but to so many other great bands/musicians that have touched your soul with music. For standing in the long lines to get into the shows, for buying tickets to support our art. For buying our merch, albums, streaming our tracks, posting photos of us, helping us spreading the word, building fan sites, getting our logos/signatures tattooed, and for just plain being kick ass fans! We’ve had a life time of fun together and consider you an extension of my family! God bless you all!! I’ve never been more inspired and excited about the future! On to the next chapter of this crazy roller coaster!! Who’s Ridin’ shotgun?? Let’s Goooooo! 👊🏼👽
.
Photo by @loreemckpics
